      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This specimen remains in pristine, showroom condition, featuring an unblemished exterior and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously curated and mechanically peerless, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a masterpiece of engineering that defies its age. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for absolute excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
