    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next big adventure. You won\u2019t find another one this clean! Shoot me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
