      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a concourse-level E46 M3, a definitive example of German engineering. The S54 inline-six features a fully overhauled VANOS system and a documented rod bearing replacement, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates with factory precision. The chassis has been professionally reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to address known structural vulnerabilities, maintaining superior torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a refreshed M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry but has been enhanced with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers for sharpened turn-in response. This vehicle presents with zero deferred maintenance, a laser-straight body, and a pristine undercarriage free of oxidation.",
